data.title: How to get to our head office in Espoo, Finland
data.meta_description: Fortum employees in the Helsinki metropolitan area are located at Keilalahdentie 2–4, 02150 Espoo. Along with Fortum, other tenants in the headquarters building include Tietoevry Oyj and Microsoft Oy.
data.text:
The Keilaniemen Kalliopysäköinti project has started, and several construction works are underway in Keilaniemi, which affect access routes in the area. It would be best if you were prepared that car and light traffic routes might change during the project and reserve some more time to arrive and leave the headquarters. The construction works themselves will take several years to complete.

You can find the latest updates on the project on the Kalliopysäköinti Facebook page.
